Edit a Figure Page <br/><br/>

You are going to have the chance to edit <%=@figure.name%>'s page. <br/>


<form method="POST" action="/figures/<%=@figure.id%>">
  <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="PATCH">

<br/>
Figure Name:<br/>
<input type="text" name="figure[name]" id="figure_name">
<br/>
<br/>
Landmarks That <%=@figure.name%> Might be associated with:<br/>
<%Landmark.all.each do |landmark|%>
<input type="checkbox" name="figure[landmark_ids][]" id="landmark_<%=landmark.id%>" value="<%=landmark.id%>" <%='checked' if @figure.landmarks.include?(landmark) %>><%=landmark.name%><br/></input><br/>
<%end%>
<br/>
Titles that <%=@figure.name%> Might be associated with:<br/>
<%Title.all.each do |title|%>
<input type="checkbox" name="figure[title_ids][]" id="title_<%=title.id%>" value="<%=title.id%>" <%='checked' if @figure.titles.include?(title) %>><%=title.name%><br/></input><br/>
<%end%>
<input type="submit" value="Edit Figure">

Or You can Submit a New Landmark or Title for this Figure:
New Landmark Name
<input type="text" name="figure[new_landmark][name]" id="new_landmark">
<input type="text" name="figure[new_landmark][year_completed" id="new_landmark_year">
New Title Name
<input type="text" name="figure[new_title]" id="new_title">
</form>
